Multimodal Security Attack Vectors. Four attack cards: 1) PROMPT INJECTION VIA IMAGE: Invisible Text (White on White) -> OCR reads -> Vision Encoder processes -> Injection executes. 2) OCR EXPLOITS: Text in Image bypasses Input Filters -> Injection reaches Model. 3) ADVERSARIAL PATCHES: Small Image Region -> Targeted Misclassification / Overlooked Objects. 4) ACOUSTIC ATTACKS: Ultrasound (>20kHz) -> Inaudible to Humans -> STT Manipulation. Defense: OCR Injection Check, Audio Frequency Filter. Red warning style, German labels.